<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?>
<FlavorTextDefs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../Schema/FlavorText.xsd">

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_MAIN</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>What foul pollutant of a creature crosses my screen?</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>What foul pollutant of a creature crosses my screen?</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>What foul pollutant of a creature crosses my screen?</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>I see even the Empire&apos;s rejects have managed to survive. I guess we can try to get along if your mood has improved.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Your deal with the ill forces of the galaxy will doom all. If it&apos;s of use, we&apos;d beseech you to reconsider your course through history.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Oh, no. I had really hoped the rumors were false.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>So, the prodigal Clan returns. Have you come to bend knee once more to the Empire? Return as our shock troops, and the universe will know the terror of a united Empire.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ARCEAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Are the Drengin bickering between themselves now? Is your desire for conflict really that boundless?</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>No matter what you call yourself, I have no mercy for Drengin.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>No! This can&apos;t be. I thought the Korath Clan was wiped out when the Empire fell.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Good, the Alliance survives. I&apos;d hate to have never been unable to exact revenge.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Know that the Korath Clan does not honor whatever mercy the Drengin Empire may have extended. No act can save you from extinction.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>The fact your frail, small kind has been allowed to survive is a testament to how weak the universe allows itself to be. We&apos;ll be sure to rectify this.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>The Empire failed! Your chains do nothing but bind you to the weak. The only course forward is annihilation! The Korath Clan will carry on the Drengin legacy. We have no use for your weakness.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_YOR</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Don&apos;t think we&apos;ll spare you just because you&apos;re made of metal. Extinction will come for you all the same, and we&apos;ll use your broken bodies to repair our weapons and ships.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You survived. Another failing of the Empire. The Korath Clan won&apos;t make the same mistake.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>We&apos;ve found you. You spent so long cowering in corners of the universe, but we won&apos;t lose you this time. The Korath Clan will finally snuff out your group of survivors.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_SEEING</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>This must be a joke. You can&apos;t possibly have survived this long.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_RESPONSE_PEACEFUL</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>I hope only some of our meetings are this hostile.</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Watch your tongue, or I&apos;ll pull it from your screaming head.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You forget the Korath Clan does not extend mercy.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Hope is a common mistake among the weak.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Ha! Weak Drengin, like those of the Empire, are no Drengin.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ARCEAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Mind yourself! The Korath Clan needs no reason to annihilate the weak.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You won&apos;t need it.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>There is nothing strong enough to wipe out the Korath Clan.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>We don&apos;t need to keep up this hostility.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>I hope you&apos;ll reconsider if given time.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You&apos;ll find us more resilient than we look. </Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Mind your tongue! You&apos;re nothing but a rebellious legion.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_YOR</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Threat registered. We anticipate a change in results.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Threaten all you like. I refuse to fear you.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>The Resistance is prepared for the worst you can manage.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_SEEING</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>We are no joke.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_RESPONSE_NEUTRAL</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>I&apos;ll wait until you&apos;re done with your tantrum.</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Laugh while you can. The Korath clan will see to your extinction soon enough.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Our course through history will be one of conquest.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Surrender and the Korath put you and your fears to rest.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You offer chains; we&apos;ll offer relief from your humiliation through death.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ARCEAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Remember this as the moment you ensured your own extinction.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>No longer bound by the Empire&apos;s rules, the Korath can finally wipe you out of existence.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>And I thought your petty Resistance had been stomped out.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Try, and I&apos;ll be happy to remind you what we did to the Empire.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Then this meeting is concluded.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You&apos;ve been beaten before; you&apos;ll be beaten again. I&apos;m not gonna worry.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>There&apos;s only one thing to do with a rabid war dog.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_YOR</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Conversation == useless. Terminate Communication.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You&apos;re hardly as threatening as you think. I&apos;m terminating this communication.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>The Resistance is familiar with your tactics. You&apos;re no threat to us.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_SEEING</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>We tire.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TAUNT_PLAYER</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Your continued resistance is futile. The Korath will see to your extinction.</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>
	
	<FlavorTextDef>
        <InternalName>DECLARE_WAR_MAIN</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Pozwoliliśmy wam marnieć wystarczająco długo. Nadszedł czas, aby rozerwać waszą cywilizację na strzępy i pozbyć się was z galaktyki![BR][BR][COLOR=UIDefaultHighlight](Jesteśmy w stanie wojny)[/COLOR]</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Wystarczająco długo byłeś cierniem w boku Drengina. Czas was zniszczyć. Za dekadę nikt nie będzie pamiętał o Sojuszu Terrańskim.[BR][BR][COLOR=UIDefaultHighlight](Jesteśmy w stanie wojny)[/COLOR]</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Wystarczająco długo unikaliście swojego losu. Korath zniszczy waszą małą bandę wyrzutków.[BR][BR][COLOR=UIDefaultHighlight](Jesteśmy w stanie wojny)[/COLOR]</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>GENERIC_GREETING</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Make this quick, alien scum.</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TRADE_OFFER_REFUSE</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Rethink that offer before I pull you apart.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TRADE_OFFER_PERFORMED</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Don&apos;t think this trade ensures your safety.</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TRADE_OFFER_WAITING</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Make this trade worth my time, or I&apos;ll forcefully take it.</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>PLAYER_TRADE_COUNTER_OFFER_HEADER</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>Well?</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>EXTRA_OPTIONS_MAIN_TEXT</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>You think yourself worthy to speak to the Korath?</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>
		
</FlavorTextDefs>